{"tid":2217820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸日記（11）見字飲水","createTime":"2020-09-25T17:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T04:51:34.000Z","uid":216380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd668e6028743e390133269b977e083b2355886f","tid":2217820,"uid":216380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"20歲仔無啦啦爆一堆上面<br />\n（爆之前好乾淨 唔太點生暗瘡）<br />\n太多暗瘡真係頂唔順 <br />\n約囡囡出街都驚對方介意<br />\n所以有副作用都照去左食A酸 回復翻個靚仔樣<br />\n<br />\n(長沙灣陳）<br />\n<br />\n咁依家食左一個禮拜左右 其實都見到有效<br />\n無咩點再紅腫 石頭瘡 都少左 <br />\n<br />\n醫生開左20mgA酸+抗生素 比我一次過食<br />\n話減低爆發期 依家都無咩點爆<br />\n <br />\n<strong> 唯一唔好就係 真係好撚乾 嘴唇 面 屎忽 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">純粹記錄下</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>4-6個月既暗瘡之旅已經開始！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n以下附圖幾張：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1KEiHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1KEiHV.jpg&h=f508886c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGha9PB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGha9PB.jpg&h=1e33e176&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70f6bdc132e159149f8796e8092384e38891713d","tid":2217820,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"睇左幾錢"},{"pid":"bd9df6cc9a8f56595f43b3a6ea5651cddc982bec","tid":2217820,"uid":216380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f6bdc132e159149f8796e8092384e38891713d","tid":2217820,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"睇左幾錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"第一次睇1220$ 計埋診金 藥就1040$"},{"pid":"1519c4d7126b3b52b4e809b735955199bd60f3f2","tid":2217820,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n我17 歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" clas